summary: Young ambitious professional with a demonstrated history of working in the event and ticketing industry. Skilled in Marketing, Music, Multilingual, Account Management, Sales and International Business Management. Graduated with a double Bachelor's degree focused in Marketing and International Business from London South Bank University and University Colleges Leuven-Limburg.
